Flaherty Says Europe Crisis Could Bring World Near a Recession

-- B y   T o r u   F u j i o k a
-- 
2011-11-16T05:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-16/flaherty-says-europe-crisis-could-bring-world-near-a-recession.html
Canadian Finance Minister  Jim Flaherty  said  Europe ’s financial crisis could bring the global
economy close to a recession.  “Concrete actions are clearly needed to deal with the
sovereign debt and banking sector crises” in Europe, Flaherty
said in a speech in  Tokyo  today. “It could even, potentially,
bring the world to the verge of another recession.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
